name: PASTEL CLOUDS
description:
By default, you start with 5 random clouds. A new cloud is generated where you click, and you can use d/D keyboard key to delete the last added cloud. When the cloud leaves the screen, it is reborn in a different form on the right side. 

Infinite animation, variable dimensions, generative, interactive - p5.js, HTML, CSS

Artist: Aleksandra Jovanic / @aleksandrajovanic  — August 2021
